#player

(current player *)
(descr *)
    Well, there you are.  On vacation at last.

    (select)

        (par) Kind of lonely.  You recall your mom's reaction when you
        planned this trip, "Why are you going on vacation alone? When
        are you going to find a nice girl and get married?"

    (or)
    (stopping)

